# Audio
## Increase volume
"pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ +1%"
 XF86AudioRaiseVolume
## Decrease volume
"pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ -1%"
 XF86AudioLowerVolume
## Mute volume
"pactl set-sink-mute @DEFAULT_SINK@ toggle"
 XF86AudioMute
## Mute microphone
"pactl set-source-mute @DEFAULT_SOURCE@ toggle"
 XF86AudioMicMute

# Backlight
## Increase Brightness
"brightnessctl s +5%"
 XF86MonBrightnessUp
### Decrease Brightness
"brightnessctl s 5%-"
 XF86MonBrightnessDown
"brightnessctl s 0%"
 Shift + XF86MonBrightnessDown
"brightnessctl s 100%"
 Shift + XF86MonBrightnessUp

# Keyboard Backlight
## Increase Brightness
"brightnessctl --device='smc::kbd_backlight' set +16"
 XF86KbdBrightnessUp
## Decrease Brightness
"brightnessctl --device='smc::kbd_backlight' set 16-"
 XF86KbdBrightnessDown
"brightnessctl --device='smc::kbd_backlight' set 0"
 Shift + XF86KbdBrightnessDown
"brightnessctl --device='smc::kbd_backlight' set 255"
 Shift + XF86KbdBrightnessUp

